videos.description: Lonzo Ball grabs Meyers Leonard's miss and throws a full-court pass to Zion Williamson for his first Christmas basket.

videos.headline: Zion lays in first Christmas bucket

videos.description: Duncan Robinson scores 12 points on four 3-pointers for the Heat in the first quarter vs. the Pelicans.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Duncan Robinson drains four 3-pointers in first quarter) 2020/12/25 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Duncan Robinson drains four 3-pointers in first quarter

videos.description: Goran Dragic grabs a rebound and passes to Bam Adebayo, who finishes with a dunk on the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Adebayo jams it down for Heat) 2020/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Adebayo jams it down for Heat

videos.description: Goran Dragic comes up with the steal and hits a nice spin move on Josh Hart before laying it in.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Dragic puts Hart in the spin cycle before layup) 2020/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dragic puts Hart in the spin cycle before layup

videos.description: Brandon Ingram goes head-to-head with Bam Adebayo and hits a 3-pointer over him.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Ingram hits heavily contested 3 over Adebayo) 2020/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ingram hits heavily contested 3 over Adebayo

videos.description: Tyler Herro drives through traffic and tosses an alley-oop up to Bam Adebayo for the jam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Herro lobs it up to Adebayo for the two-handed slam) 2020/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Herro lobs it up to Adebayo for the two-handed slam

videos.description: Zion Williamson powers through the lane on back-to-back possessions to cut into the Heat's lead.
videos.headline: Zion scores back-to-back buckets

videos.description: Brandon Ingram drives through the lane and switches up midair for the reverse layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Ingram hits smooth reverse lay-in) 2020/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ingram hits smooth reverse lay-in

videos.description: Brandon Ingram finishes the third quarter hot with a 3-pointer.

videos.headline: Ingram knocks down 3 to keep Pelicans within reach

videos.description: Goran Dragic picks off Brandon Ingram's pass and goes coast-to-coast to hit the lay-in.

videos.headline: Dragic shows off his handles for nifty layup

videos.description: Zion Williamson scores a game-high 32 points and grabs 14 rebounds in his first NBA Christmas Day game.
